### Settings ###

vbell off
vbell_msg "Ring"
altscreen on
escape ^Bb               # Use ctrl+b as esc_char

### Behaviors ###

autodetach on
startup_message off      # Turn off the splash screen
defscrollback 50000      # 50,000 lines for buffer

### Right/Left Bindings ###

bindkey "^[[c" next
bindkey "^[[d" prev
bindkey "^[[b" focus

